When a payment is unsuccessful.

Attribute | Description
--------- | -----------
`type` | `bill.payment.failed`
`payload.data.company` | The [company](#the-company-object) linked to this resource.
`payload.data.paymentMethod` | The [payment method](#the-payment-method-object) linked to the payment.
`payload.data.amount` | The amount of the unsuccesful payment.
